name: Stirrup-css
tagline: CSS3 flexbox responsive grid that can be used as a drop-in replacement for the Bootstrap 3 grid, or as a standalone flexbox grid system
body:
# Stirrup-CSS

Stirrup is a simple CSS flexbox responsive grid system. Its aimed to be used as a drop-in replacement for the Bootstrap 3 Grid system, or as a stand-alone responsive grid system.

More docs coming...
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
